{Panthos}

    Turning the panther bot rose and walked away from Cheetara his strides
moving him northward, looking back over his shoulder his head shook, "I came
in a shuttle, not a pod. I'm a factor outside Predacon and Maximal..."

Turning back northward the panther bot walked off heading north to where his
scanners had detected moving maximal signatures. Maximal City didn't seem to
be as deserted as his first approach had shown, his thoughts spiralled back
to his old decpticon days, havoc was much easier to accomplish those times.
Blow up a stupid earthling damn and watch the autobots scurry around trying
to save everything. But in this time there were no "humans".

His scans had picked up the bio signatures of their ancestors but he felt no
desire to try and destroy them. They were too primitive and too easy a
target. Transformer havoc would be his dish of choice here. First neutral,
then maximal and finally havoc within the predacon ranks... Smiling to
himself he let his thoughts drift to the joys of chaos...
